{"tid":2344824,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"過百英國遊客連夜酒店偷走拒隔離 瑞士舉國震怒","createTime":"2020-12-29T05:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T08:31:11.000Z","uid":66087,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c55af06fad12e8f4d2fac9c36bd61f61c9d1f5","tid":2344824,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ooBABRV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FooBABRV.jpg&h=38482b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n變種新冠病毒持續蔓延，多國因應疫情對英國封關或加強防疫措施，其中瑞士要求來自英國的遊客自我隔離十天，但據報數百名英國遊客在隔離期間逃走。<br />\n<br />\n有「小倫敦」之稱的瑞士滑雪勝地韋爾比耶，冬季有五分一的遊客來自英國。韋爾比耶所在的巴涅地方政府發言人桑多斯表示，當局追查到有420個遊客需要在聖誕節前接受隔離。<br />\n<br />\n不過「隔離令」下達後，有50個遊客立即離開，餘下的大部分人只隔離了一天就漏夜逃跑。有些人之後現身法國，至周日只餘下不足十二人仍然進行隔離。<br />\n<br />\n英國遊客偷走過程神不知鬼不覺，酒店方面說，直到他們沒有接聽房間電話，放在房門外的餐點亦絲毫未動才發現他們已離開。<br />\n<br />\n桑多斯批評政府倉卒要求來自英國的遊客隔離，他們的憤怒可以理解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCoronavirus: Hundreds of British skiers flee Swiss Verbier quarantine<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55465079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-55465079&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=51424531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-55465079&h=6e36ab3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55465079</a>"},{"pid":"7adddf46be781b99cf0ee2b662102f7fe8d8335c","tid":2344824,"uid":283240,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:12:24.000Z","msg":"兒登仔又扮睇唔到外國勢力蝗"},{"pid":"368ca33af32b00cdf3baadeea1dc608b91fc8074","tid":2344824,"uid":269061,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"19 點睇"},{"pid":"37fd4390a437c59f13548f1bdcc422ce779aebd9","tid":2344824,"uid":56238,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7adddf46be781b99cf0ee2b662102f7fe8d8335c","tid":2344824,"uid":283240,"like":7,"dislike":